---
import Layout from '@/layouts/Layout.astro';
---
<Layout title="Automatización documental | IA y automatización" description="Conectamos tus fuentes de datos con tus plantillas y generamos documentos correctos en segundos, sin intervención manual.">

  <div class="ad-page">

  <!-- HERO -->
  <section class="ad-hero">
    <div class="container-libera ad-hero-grid">
      <div class="ad-hero-copy">
        <h1 class="ad-title">Los documentos que tardas una hora en hacer, <em>listos en segundos</em></h1>
        <p class="ad-lead">Cotizaciones, contratos, informes, resúmenes de reunión, reportes de avance. Documentos que siguen la misma estructura, con datos que ya existen en algún sistema, y que alguien tiene que armar a mano de todos modos. La automatización documental conecta la fuente de datos con la plantilla y genera el documento sin intervención. Correcto, formateado y listo para enviar.</p>
        <ul class="ad-icons">
          <li>
            <span class="ad-ex-icon">
              <svg width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M14 2H6a2 2 0 0 0-2 2v16a2 2 0 0 0 2 2h12a2 2 0 0 0 2-2V8z"/><polyline points="14 2 14 8 20 8"/></svg>
            </span>
            <div>
              <p class="ad-ex-ttl">Google Docs, Word, PDF y más</p>
              <p class="ad-ex-ds">El documento final en el formato que ya usa tu equipo</p>
            </div>
          </li>
          <li>
            <span class="ad-ex-icon">
              <svg width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><ellipse cx="12" cy="5" rx="9" ry="3"/><path d="M21 12c0 1.66-4 3-9 3s-9-1.34-9-3"/><path d="M3 5v14c0 1.66 4 3 9 3s9-1.34 9-3V5"/></svg>
            </span>
            <div>
              <p class="ad-ex-ttl">Datos desde CRM, formularios y bases de datos</p>
              <p class="ad-ex-ds">Sin copiar y pegar — los datos llegan solos a la plantilla</p>
            </div>
          </li>
          <li>
            <span class="ad-ex-icon">
              <svg width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M20 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-4-4H8a4 4 0 0 0-4 4v2"/><circle cx="12" cy="7" r="4"/></svg>
            </span>
            <div>
              <p class="ad-ex-ttl">Revisión humana opcional</p>
              <p class="ad-ex-ds">Se genera y revisa antes de enviar, o va directo si el flujo es confiable</p>
            </div>
          </li>
          <li>
            <span class="ad-ex-icon">
              <svg width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/><polyline points="12 6 12 12 16 14"/></svg>
            </span>
            <div>
              <p class="ad-ex-ttl">Segundos, no minutos</p>
              <p class="ad-ex-ds">El tiempo de generación es irrelevante — ocurre mientras haces otra cosa</p>
            </div>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <!-- MOCK: pipeline documental -->
      <div class="ad-mock" aria-hidden="true">
        <div class="ad-mock-header">
          <span class="ad-mock-dot" style="background:#ef4444"></span>
          <span class="ad-mock-dot" style="background:#f59e0b"></span>
          <span class="ad-mock-dot" style="background:#22c55e"></span>
          <span class="ad-mock-label">Automatización documental</span>
          <span class="ad-mock-sub">Generación inteligente de documentos en segundos</span>
        </div>
        <div class="ad-mock-body">
          <!-- Fuentes -->
          <div class="ad-mock-col ad-mock-sources">
            <div class="ad-mock-source">
              <span class="ad-src-icon" style="background:#dbeafe; color:#3b82f6">
                <svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M17.5 19H9a7 7 0 1 1 6.71-9h1.79a4.5 4.5 0 1 1 0 9z"/></svg>
              </span>
              <div>
                <p class="ad-src-name">CRM</p>
                <p class="ad-src-desc">Datos de clientes, ventas y oportunidades</p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="ad-mock-source">
              <span class="ad-src-icon" style="background:#dcfce7; color:#16a34a">
                <svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><rect x="3" y="3" width="18" height="18" rx="2"/><path d="M3 9h18M9 21V9"/></svg>
              </span>
              <div>
                <p class="ad-src-name">Formulario web</p>
                <p class="ad-src-desc">Respuestas y datos ingresados</p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="ad-mock-source">
              <span class="ad-src-icon" style="background:#e0e7ff; color:#6366f1">
                <svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><ellipse cx="12" cy="5" rx="9" ry="3"/><path d="M21 12c0 1.66-4 3-9 3s-9-1.34-9-3"/><path d="M3 5v14c0 1.66 4 3 9 3s9-1.34 9-3V5"/></svg>
              </span>
              <div>
                <p class="ad-src-name">Base de datos</p>
                <p class="ad-src-desc">Información estructurada y transaccional</p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="ad-mock-source">
              <span class="ad-src-icon" style="background:#fef3c7; color:#d97706">
                <svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M12 1a3 3 0 0 0-3 3v8a3 3 0 0 0 6 0V4a3 3 0 0 0-3-3z"/><path d="M19 10v2a7 7 0 0 1-14 0v-2"/><line x1="12" y1="19" x2="12" y2="23"/><line x1="8" y1="23" x2="16" y2="23"/></svg>
              </span>
              <div>
                <p class="ad-src-name">Transcripción / Reunión</p>
                <p class="ad-src-desc">Notas y contenido de la conversación</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- Centro: motor -->
          <div class="ad-mock-col ad-mock-center">
            <div class="ad-mock-engine">
              <div class="ad-engine-icon">
                <svg width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M14 2H6a2 2 0 0 0-2 2v16a2 2 0 0 0 2 2h12a2 2 0 0 0 2-2V8z"/><polyline points="14 2 14 8 20 8"/><line x1="16" y1="13" x2="8" y2="13"/><line x1="16" y1="17" x2="8" y2="17"/><polyline points="10 9 9 9 8 9"/></svg>
              </div>
              <p class="ad-engine-title">Plantilla + datos</p>
              <p class="ad-engine-sub">Motor documental</p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- Outputs -->
          <div class="ad-mock-col ad-mock-outputs">
            <div class="ad-mock-output">
              <span class="ad-out-badge" style="background:#dcfce7; color:#16a34a">.DOCX</span>
              <p class="ad-out-name">Cotización</p>
            </div>
            <div class="ad-mock-output">
              <span class="ad-out-badge" style="background:#fee2e2; color:#ef4444">.PDF</span>
              <p class="ad-out-name">Contrato</p>
            </div>
            <div class="ad-mock-output">
              <span class="ad-out-badge" style="background:#fef3c7; color:#d97706">.PPTX</span>
              <p class="ad-out-name">Reporte</p>
            </div>
            <div class="ad-mock-output">
              <span class="ad-out-badge" style="background:#ede9fe; color:#7c3aed">.DOCX</span>
              <p class="ad-out-name">Resumen</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="ad-mock-footer">
          <svg width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#ea580c" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M22 11.08V12a10 10 0 1 1-5.93-9.14"/><polyline points="22 4 12 14.01 9 11.01"/></svg>
          <span>Genera documentos correctos, formateados y listos para enviar.</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CONTENT -->
  <section class="ad-content">
    <div class="container-libera ad-content-grid">
      <!-- Sinistra: Dónde aplica -->
      <div class="ad-body">
        <h2 class="ad-section-title">Dónde aplica</h2>
        <p>Cualquier documento repetitivo que siga una estructura y cambie solo en los datos es candidato a automatizarse.</p>
        <ul class="ad-apply-list">
          <li>
            <span class="ad-ex-icon">
              <svg width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><line x1="12" y1="5" x2="12" y2="19"/><polyline points="19 12 12 19 5 12"/></svg>
            </span>
            <p>Propuestas comerciales con datos variables</p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <span class="ad-ex-icon">
              <svg width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M14 2H6a2 2 0 0 0-2 2v16a2 2 0 0 0 2 2h12a2 2 0 0 0 2-2V8z"/><polyline points="14 2 14 8 20 8"/></svg>
            </span>
            <p>Contratos con fechas y datos de las partes</p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <span class="ad-ex-icon">
              <svg width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><line x1="18" y1="20" x2="18" y2="10"/><line x1="12" y1="20" x2="12" y2="4"/><line x1="6" y1="20" x2="6" y2="14"/></svg>
            </span>
            <p>Reportes mensuales con métricas de distintas fuentes</p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <span class="ad-ex-icon">
              <svg width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M12 1a3 3 0 0 0-3 3v8a3 3 0 0 0 6 0V4a3 3 0 0 0-3-3z"/><path d="M19 10v2a7 7 0 0 1-14 0v-2"/></svg>
            </span>
            <p>Resúmenes de llamada o reunión desde transcripciones</p>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <!-- Destra: El proceso (cerchi numerati) -->
      <div class="ad-process">
        <h2 class="ad-section-title">El proceso</h2>
        <ol class="ad-steps">
          <li>
            <span class="ad-num">1</span>
            <p>Identificamos los documentos que tu equipo repite más.</p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <span class="ad-num">2</span>
            <p>Mapeamos qué datos necesita cada uno y de dónde vienen.</p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <span class="ad-num">3</span>
            <p>Construimos la plantilla estructurada y el flujo de generación.</p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <span class="ad-num">4</span>
            <p>El documento se genera con un clic o de forma automática.</p>
          </li>
        </ol>
        <p class="ad-process-closing"><strong>El equipo deja de formatear. <em>Empieza a firmar.</em></strong></p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- PUNTOS CLAVE -->
  <section class="ad-features">
    <div class="container-libera">
      <h2 class="ad-features-title">
        <svg width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg>
        Puntos clave
      </h2>
      <div class="ad-grid">
        <div class="ad-fi">
          <svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="var(--orange)" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M14 2H6a2 2 0 0 0-2 2v16a2 2 0 0 0 2 2h12a2 2 0 0 0 2-2V8z"/><polyline points="14 2 14 8 20 8"/></svg>
          <div><strong>Formato flexible</strong><br/>Compatible con Google Docs, Microsoft Word, PDF o el formato que ya usa tu equipo</div>
        </div>
        <div class="ad-fi">
          <svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="var(--orange)" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><ellipse cx="12" cy="5" rx="9" ry="3"/><path d="M21 12c0 1.66-4 3-9 3s-9-1.34-9-3"/><path d="M3 5v14c0 1.66 4 3 9 3s9-1.34 9-3V5"/></svg>
          <div><strong>Datos desde tus sistemas</strong><br/>Los toma de tu CRM, formularios o bases de datos existentes</div>
        </div>
        <div class="ad-fi">
          <svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="var(--orange)" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M20 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-4-4H8a4 4 0 0 0-4 4v2"/><circle cx="12" cy="7" r="4"/></svg>
          <div><strong>Revisión humana opcional</strong><br/>Antes del envío final, si el proceso lo requiere</div>
        </div>
        <div class="ad-fi">
          <svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="var(--orange)" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/><polyline points="12 6 12 12 16 14"/></svg>
          <div><strong>Velocidad real</strong><br/>Tiempo de generación: segundos, no minutos</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA -->
  <section class="ad-cta">
    <div class="container-libera">
      <div class="ad-cta-inner">
        <div class="ad-cta-left">
          <div class="ad-cta-icon">
            <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="var(--orange)" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M14 2H6a2 2 0 0 0-2 2v16a2 2 0 0 0 2 2h12a2 2 0 0 0 2-2V8z"/><polyline points="14 2 14 8 20 8"/><line x1="16" y1="13" x2="8" y2="13"/><line x1="16" y1="17" x2="8" y2="17"/></svg>
          </div>
          <div class="ad-cta-text">
            <p>Si tu equipo genera los mismos documentos una y otra vez,<br/><em>hay una forma más rápida.</em></p>
            <p>Exploramos tu operación, identificamos qué documentos se pueden automatizar y te mostramos cómo implementarlo.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <a href="/diagnostico" class="btn-primary ad-cta-btn">Solicitar diagnóstico <span aria-hidden="true">›</span></a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  </div>

<style>
  /* BREADCRUMB */
  .ad-bc {
    display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 0.5rem;
    padding-top: calc(var(--nav-height) + 2.5rem);
    font-size: 0.8rem; color: var(--text-secondary);
  }
  .ad-bc a { color: var(--text-secondary); transition: color 0.2s; }
  .ad-bc a:hover { color: var(--orange); }
  .ad-bc [aria-current="page"] { color: var(--orange); font-weight: 600; }

  /* HERO */
  .ad-hero {
    padding-top: calc(var(--nav-height) + clamp(4rem, 5vw, 5rem));
    padding-bottom: clamp(3rem, 6vw, 5rem);
  }
  .ad-hero-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: minmax(0, 1fr) minmax(0, 1.3fr);
    gap: clamp(2rem, 5vw, 4.5rem);
    align-items: start;
  }
  .ad-title {
    font-size: clamp(1.75rem, 3.5vw, 2.75rem);
    line-height: 1.1;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }
  .ad-title em { font-style: normal; color: var(--orange); }
  .ad-lead {
    font-size: clamp(0.9rem, 1.15vw, 1rem);
    line-height: 1.75;
    max-width: 46ch;
    margin-bottom: 1.75rem;
    color: var(--text-secondary);
  }
  .ad-icons { list-style: none; margin: 0; padding: 0; display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 0.75rem; }
  .ad-icons li { display: flex; align-items: flex-start; gap: 0.75rem; }
  .ad-ex-icon {
    display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
    width: 2rem; height: 2rem; border-radius: 0.375rem; flex-shrink: 0;
    background: oklch(98.5% 0.008 55); color: var(--orange); margin-top: 0.05rem;
  }
  .ad-ex-ttl { font-size: 0.9rem; font-weight: 700; color: var(--text-primary); margin: 0 0 0.2rem; }
  .ad-ex-ds  { font-size: 0.85rem; color: var(--text-secondary); line-height: 1.5; margin: 0; }

  /* MOCK */
  .ad-mock {
    border: 1px solid rgba(0,48,73,0.1);
    border-radius: 0.75rem;
    overflow: hidden;
    background: #fff;
    box-shadow: 0 8px 40px oklch(0% 0 0 / 0.12);
  }
  .ad-mock-header {
    display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 0.5rem;
    padding: 0.75rem 1rem;
    background: oklch(98% 0.004 240);
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }
  .ad-mock-dot { width: 0.5rem; height: 0.5rem; border-radius: 50%; }
  .ad-mock-label { font-size: 0.78rem; font-weight: 700; color: var(--text-primary); margin-left: 0.25rem; }
  .ad-mock-sub { font-size: 0.72rem; color: var(--text-secondary); margin-left: auto; }

  .ad-mock-body {
    display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr auto 1fr;
    gap: 0.5rem; padding: 1rem;
    align-items: center;
  }
  .ad-mock-col { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 0.5rem; }

  .ad-mock-source {
    display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 0.5rem;
    padding: 0.5rem 0.6rem;
    border: 1px solid var(--border); border-radius: 0.375rem;
    background: #fafafa;
  }
  .ad-src-icon {
    display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
    width: 1.75rem; height: 1.75rem; border-radius: 0.25rem; flex-shrink: 0;
  }
  .ad-src-name { font-size: 0.72rem; font-weight: 700; color: var(--text-primary); margin: 0 0 0.1rem; }
  .ad-src-desc { font-size: 0.65rem; color: var(--text-secondary); margin: 0; line-height: 1.3; }

  .ad-mock-center { align-items: center; }
  .ad-mock-engine {
    display: flex; flex-direction: column; align-items: center; gap: 0.25rem;
    padding: 0.75rem 1rem;
    background: oklch(98.5% 0.008 55);
    border: 1px solid oklch(90% 0.02 55);
    border-radius: 0.5rem;
  }
  .ad-engine-icon { color: var(--orange); }
  .ad-engine-title { font-size: 0.72rem; font-weight: 700; color: var(--text-primary); margin: 0; text-align: center; }
  .ad-engine-sub { font-size: 0.65rem; color: var(--text-secondary); margin: 0; text-align: center; }

  .ad-mock-output {
    display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 0.5rem;
    padding: 0.5rem 0.75rem;
    border: 1px solid var(--border); border-radius: 0.375rem;
    background: #fafafa;
  }
  .ad-out-badge {
    font-size: 0.6rem; font-weight: 700; padding: 0.1rem 0.35rem;
    border-radius: 0.2rem; letter-spacing: 0.03em; font-family: var(--font-mono);
  }
  .ad-out-name { font-size: 0.75rem; font-weight: 600; color: var(--text-primary); margin: 0; }

  .ad-mock-footer {
    display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 0.5rem;
    padding: 0.625rem 1rem;
    background: oklch(98.5% 0.008 55);
    border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
    font-size: 0.75rem; color: var(--text-secondary);
  }

  /* CONTENT */
  .ad-content { padding-block: clamp(2.5rem, 5vw, 4rem); background: #fff; }
  .ad-content-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: minmax(0, 1fr) minmax(0, 1fr);
    gap: clamp(2rem, 5vw, 5rem);
    align-items: start;
  }
  .ad-section-title {
    font-size: clamp(1.1rem, 1.8vw, 1.35rem);
    font-weight: 700; color: var(--text-primary);
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
  }
  .ad-body p, .ad-process p { color: var(--text-secondary); font-size: 0.95rem; line-height: 1.75; margin: 0 0 1rem; }
  .ad-apply-list { list-style: none; margin: 0; padding: 0; display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 0.6rem; }
  .ad-apply-list li { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 0.6rem; font-size: 0.9rem; color: var(--text-secondary); }

  .ad-steps { list-style: none; margin: 0; padding: 0; display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 0.75rem; }
  .ad-steps li { display: flex; align-items: flex-start; gap: 0.75rem; font-size: 0.9rem; color: var(--text-secondary); }
  .ad-num {
    display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
    width: 2rem; height: 2rem; border-radius: 50%; flex-shrink: 0;
    border: 1.5px solid var(--orange);
    font-family: var(--font-mono); font-size: 0.7rem; font-weight: 700; color: var(--orange);
  }
  .ad-process-closing {
    margin-top: 1.25rem; font-size: 0.95rem;
    color: var(--text-primary) !important;
  }
  .ad-process-closing em { font-style: normal; color: var(--orange); }

  /* FEATURES */
  .ad-features { padding-block: clamp(2rem, 4vw, 3.5rem); background: var(--surface-alt); }
  .ad-features-title {
    font-family: var(--font-display); font-size: clamp(1.1rem, 1.8vw, 1.35rem);
    font-weight: 700; color: var(--orange); margin-bottom: 1.75rem;
    display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 0.75rem;
  }
  .ad-features-title::after { content: ""; flex: 1; height: 1px; background: var(--border); }
  .ad-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr); gap: 1.25rem 2rem; }
  .ad-fi { display: flex; align-items: flex-start; gap: 0.65rem; }
  .ad-fi svg { flex-shrink: 0; margin-top: 0.1rem; }
  .ad-fi div { font-size: 0.88rem; color: var(--text-secondary); line-height: 1.5; }
  .ad-fi strong { color: var(--text-primary); display: block; }

  /* CTA */
